Code of ethics for large us company that prides itself on innovative technologies.

1.	Principle of Transparency 
The company shall ensure transparency in its operations to the public.

2.	Principle of Data Minimization and Anonymization
The company shall collect only necessary data.

3.	Principle of Beneficence
The company will prioritize the well-being of the public, ensuring their technology does not cause harm.

4.	Principle of Public Interest and Social responsibility
The company will ensure that the deployment of technology serves the public interest and contributes positively to society.

5.	Principle of Accountability and Governance
The company shall establish clear accountability mechanisms, governance structures and ensure ethical deployment and use of technology.

